    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The `attach` subcommand uses ipc by default and looks for the endpoint on the default location. If the geth node was started with a custom `datadir` and/or `ipcpath` you must specify this path. The preferred way is:\n\n`geth attach ipc:/some/path`\n\nFor more information (e.g. how to attach over http/rpc) and an explanation about the differences between `console` and `attach` see the wiki: https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/wiki/JavaScript-Console\n",
