    "body": "Currently the flags are not defined on a subcommand but on the geth command. Removing it just for the attach subcommand is therefore not possible. This is known limitation and internally discussed. In the future we are planning to do a more git like approach where arguments are passed behind the subcommand (e.g. `git rebase --continue`). That will allow us to specify only valid flags for a subcommand.\n",
